title: East of West: 1908-2064 Timeline Poster Joins (Dgtl''300+150|MM)
description:
Overview:  <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/East_of_West" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/East_of_West</a>



Contains:   The 7-page timeline from last year's "East of West: The World"
            special, landscape-joined.

            I included both a full-scale (300 dpi, 15k x 2.5k) and a perhaps
            more practical half-scale (150 dpi, 7.5k x 1.25k) version.

            If you already read the original release, you'll be aware that that
            one does already contain such a join, but that at less than 100 dpi
            that one's more or less illegible and therefore pretty much useless
